# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Code signing
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# NEVER commit private keys (.pfx). Package.ps1 regenerates them under certs/.
# Public .cer is also ignored in-repo by default; ship it only in GitHub Release
# assets next to the MSIX (Install-LinuxDo.ps1 trusts LinuxDo-Signing.cer).
#
# Keep certs/README.md tracked (docs only).
certs/*
!certs/README.md
!certs/.gitignore
*.pfx
*.p12
*.key
